Package: interfacer
Title: Define and Enforce Interface Contracts for Dataframes
Version: 0.1.5
Authors@R: 
    person("Rob", "Challen", , "rob.challen@bristol.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5504-7768"))
Description: Allow a specification for a dataframe to be used in function 
  definitions and documentation. Performs default checks that column names and 
  datatypes are as expected, and provide a generic way to rename adapt different 
  dataframes to an interface contract.
